<style>
  .services {
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    max-width: var(--max-width);
    margin-inline: auto;

    & h1 {
      text-align: center;
      padding-block-end: 2rem;      
    }

    & a.link {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-block-start: 1rem;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      background-color: var(--light-gray);
      padding: 0.5rem 1.25rem;
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
      text-decoration: none;            
    }
  }

  .service-section {
    display: flex;
    margin-block-end: 4rem;

    & h2 {
      margin-block-end: 1rem;
    }

    & h3 {
      margin-block: 0.5rem;
    }

    & p {
      margin-block-end: 1rem;
    }

    & img {
      width: 40%;
      border-radius: 12px;
      object-fit: cover;
    }

    & li {
      position: relative;
      padding-inline-start: 30px;
    }

    & li::before {
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      content: "•";
      color: var(--blue);
    }
  }

  .right-image {
    flex-direction: row-reverse;
  }

  .service-text {
    padding-inline: 2rem;
  }
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .service-section {
      flex-direction: column;

      & img {
        width: 100%;
        height: auto;        
        flex: 0 0 auto;
        margin: 2rem 0;
        border-radius: 12px;
        object-fit: cover;
      }
    }
  }
</style>

<section class="services">
  <h1 class="header-1">{{ title }}</h1>

  <div class="service-section">
    <div class="service-text">
      <h2 class="header-2" id="ux-audit">UX Audit &amp; Usability Testing</h2>
      <p>
        A UX audit helps uncover pain points in your website or app that may hinder usability or prevent conversions. By
        identifying and addressing these issues, we improve both the user experience and your business outcomes.
      </p>
      <h3>Basic UX audit</h3>
      <p>A fast, heuristic-based evaluation to uncover key usability issues.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Review of your website or app using proven usability heuristics</li>
        <li>Annotated screenshots highlighting specific problems and recommendations</li>
        <li>Practical, prioritized suggestions to improve UX quickly</li>
      </ul>
      <h3>Advanced UX audit</h3>
      <p>A deeper analysis informed by real user behavior.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Includes everything in the Basic Audit</li>
        <li>4–8 moderated usability test sessions with your target audience</li>
        <li>A detailed report with key findings, patterns, and actionable design suggestions</li>
        <li>Optional: review of analytics data to uncover behavioral insights (if available)</li>
      </ul>
