        applications. Whether you’re starting with a rough idea or solving a specific problem, I guide you through a
        structured design process that turns concepts into testable solutions.
      </p>

      <p>
        Using the Double Diamond methodology, I explore, define, and iterate quickly — ensuring that design decisions
        are user-informed and business-aligned.
      </p>

      <p>
        I create interactive, high-fidelity prototypes in Figma, which allow for fast feedback, clear communication, and
        smoother developer handoffs. My focus is always on practical, result-driven design that improves usability,
        supports business goals, and minimizes development risk.
      </p>
      <a class="link" href="#contact">Contact</a>
    </div>
