        <a href="https://www.11ty.dev/" target="_blank">11ty (Eleventy)</a>.
      </p>

      <p>
        Unlike traditional WordPress sites, static websites are lightweight, secure by default, and require no
        server-side maintenance.
      </p>

      <p>
