        static-first architectures that deliver excellent performance and user experience. This service is ideal for
        portfolios, small business websites, or documentation pages that need to load fast, stay secure, and be
        cost-effective to host.
      </p>
       <a class="link" href="#contact">Contact</a>
    </div>
    <img src="/images/services/development-second.webp" alt="Web development" />
